        public char toCompactRepresentation()
        Obtain a compact character representation of the transaction type. This compact representation is useful for efficient database storage of this field.
        Returns:
        A single character describing the transaction type. This may be one of C,R,U or D which represent Create, Read, Update and Delete respectively.
